title: Part E
stimulusHtml:
2 points are earned: For a good, specific improvement

1 point is earned: For an explanation of how this would improve accuracy

Example: Do several trials for each value of D and take averages. This reduces personal and random error.

One point could be earned for less appropriate or less specific answers, for example “do trials in a vacuum” or “cut down on air resistance.”
